    <etym xml:lang="ru">Вероятно, из %iæ-cæm%i, где <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æ-"/> — негативная
        частица, а %i*cæm%i — какое-то забытое слово со значением ‘движение’, ‘жизнь’ и т. п.; ср.
            <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/><w>čam</w><gloss><q>движение, покачивание при
                ходьбе</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/><note type="comment"
                xml:lang="ru">а также</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"
                    >also</note><gloss><q>душа</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"
                    ><w/><gloss><q>энергия</q></gloss></mentioned>, .</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">Probably, from %iæ-cæm%i, where <ref type="xr" target="#entry_æ-"/> is a
        negative particle and %i*cæm%i is some forgotten word with the meaning ‘movement’, ‘life’,
        etc .; cf. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/><w>čam</w><gloss><q>movement, swaying when
                    walking</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/><note type="comment"
